</td><td align="center">0.228</td><td align="center">0.381<break/>(0.081, 1.794)</td><td align="center">0.222</td></tr><tr><td align="center">GG</td><td/><td align="center">144</td><td align="center">77.84%</td><td align="center">41</td><td align="center">57.75%</td><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td align="center">GA/AA</td><td/><td align="center">41</td><td align="center">22.16%</td><td align="center">30</td><td align="center">42.25%</td><td align="center">0.365<break/>(0.205, 0.650)</td><td align="center">0.001</td><td align="center">0.370<break/>(0.207, 0.661)</td><td align="center">0.001</td></tr></tbody></table><table-wrap-foot><p><sup>a </sup>= The adjusted OR was adjusted for age and gender. CI = confidence interval; OR = odds ratio.</p></table-wrap-foot></table-wrap><table-wrap id="T3" position="float"><label>Table 3</label><caption><p>Genotype frequencies for --550 in mannose-binding lectin between patients and controls and between septic patients</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><thead><tr><th align="center">Locus</th><th align="center">Allele</th><th align="center" colspan="2">Group<break/>n (%)</th><th align="center" colspan="2">Group<break/>n (%)</th><th align="center">OR<break/>(95% CI)</th><th align="center"><italic>P</italic></th><th align="center">Adjusted OR<sup>a</sup><break/>(95% CI)</th><th align="center"><italic>P</italic></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td/><td/><td align="center" colspan="2">Sepsis</td><td align="center" colspan="2">Control</td><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td align="center">GG</td><td align="center">H</td><td align="center">77</td><td align="center">30.20</td><td align="center">124</td><td align="center">31.16</td><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td align="center">GC</td><td/><td align="center">122</td><td align="center">47.84</td><td align="center">182</td><td align="center">45.73</td><td align="center">1.079<break/>(0.749, 1.556)</td><td align="center">0.682</td><td align="center">1.060<break/>(0.783, 3.598)</td>